{"word":"γραφή","slug":"γραφή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γραφή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γράφω\">γράφω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only in reference to the scriptures of Israel, namely the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ OT\">OT</a>, <b><i>scripture</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as an individual citation <b><a href='B:480 12:10'>Mk 12:10</a>; <a href='B:490 4:21'>Lk 4:21</a>; <a href='B:500 13:18'>J 13:18</a>; <a href='B:510 1:16'>Ac 1:16</a>; <a href='B:520 11:2'>Ro 11:2</a>; <a href='B:610 5:18'>1 Ti 5:18</a>; <a href='B:620 3:16'>2 Ti 3:16</a>; <a href='B:660 2:8'>Js 2:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as a body of writings <b><a href='B:470 21:42'>Mt 21:42</a>; <a href='B:480 12:24'>Mk 12:24</a>; <a href='B:490 24:27'>Lk 24:27</a>; <a href='B:500 5:39'>J 5:39</a>; <a href='B:510 17:2'>Ac 17:2</a>, <a href='B:510 17:11'>11</a>; <a href='B:520 1:2'>Ro 1:2</a>; <a href='B:520 15:4'>15:4</a>; <a href='B:530 15:3'>1 Cor 15:3</a>; <a href='B:550 3:8'>Gal 3:8</a>; <a href='B:680 3:16'>2 Pt 3:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γραπτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:γράφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}